div class="t m0 x1b h4 ycd ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">以前北大有一个部长的儿子，<span class="_ _9"></span>读书时，<span class="_ _9"></span>他每天有奔驰车</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y56 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">接送，<span class="_ _7"></span>同学们都非常羡慕。<span class="_ _e"></span>毕业后，<span class="_ _7"></span>他顺利地踏上仕途。<span class="_ _e"></span>然</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ya8 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">而好景不长，<span class="_ _7"></span>他的父亲因故倒台，<span class="_ _7"></span>他也随之失去了高位，<span class="_ _7"></span>由</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ya9 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">于无法面对这种现实，最终他选择了自杀。 </div><div class="t m0 x1b h4 yaa ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls20 ws0">另外，卡扎菲担任利比亚总统长达<span class="_ _13"> </span>42<span class="_ _13"> </span>年，是阿拉伯国</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
